ah%20and%20the%20elders%20of%20the%20Jews%20in%20their%20work.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_6_8%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BMoreover%2C%20I%20hereby%20decree%20that%20you%20are%20to%20help%20these%20elders%20of%20the%20Jews%20as%20they%20rebuild%20this%20Temple%20of%20God.%20You%20must%20pay%20the%20full%20construction%20costs%2C%20without%20delay%2C%20from%20my%20taxes%20collected%20in%20the%20province%20west%20of%20the%20Euphrates%20River%20so%20that%20the%20work%20will%20not%20be%20interrupted.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_6_9%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BGive%20the%20priests%20in%20Jerusalem%20whatever%20is%20needed%20in%20the%20way%20of%20young%20bulls%2C%20rams%2C%20and%20male%20lambs%20for%20the%20burnt%20offerings%20presented%20to%20the%20God%20of%20heaven.%20And%20without%20fail%2C%20provide%20them%20with%20as%20much%20wheat%2C%20salt%2C%20wine%2C%20and%20olive%20oil%20as%20they%20need%20each%20day.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_6_10%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20they%20will%20be%20able%20to%20offer%20acceptable%20sacrifices%20to%20the%20God%20of%20heaven%20and%20pray%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20king%20and%20his%20sons.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_6_11%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThose%20who%20violate%20this%20decree%20in%20any%20way%20will%20have%20a%20beam%20pulled%20from%20their%20house.%20Then%20they%20will%20be%20lifted%20up%20and%20impaled%20on%20it%2C%20and%20their%20house%20will%20be%20reduced%20to%20a%20pile%20of%20rubble.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E6%3A11%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Aramaic%20%3Cem%3Ea%20dunghill.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_6_12%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EMay%20the%20God%20who%20has%20chosen%20the%20city%20of%20Jerusalem%20as%20the%20place%20to%20honor%20his%20name%20destroy%20any%20king%20or%20nation%20that%20violates%20this%20command%20and%20destroys%20this%20Temple.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BI%2C%20Darius%2C%20have%20issued%20this%20decree.%20Let%20it%20be%20obeyed%20with%20all%20diligence.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_6_13%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20Temple%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Dedication%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3ETattenai%2C%20governor%20of%20the%20province%20west%20of%20the%20Euphrates%20River%2C%20and%20Shethar-bozenai%20and%20their%20colleagues%20complied%20at%20once%20with%20the%20command%20of%20King%20Darius.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_6_14%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20the%20Jewish%20elders%20continued%20their%20work%2C%20and%20they%20were%20greatly%20encouraged%20by%20the%20preaching%20of%20the%20prophets%20Haggai%20and%20Zechariah%20son%20of%20Iddo.%20The%20Temple%20was%20finally%20finished%2C%20as%20had%20been%20commanded%20by%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%20and%20decreed%20by%20Cyrus%2C%20Darius%2C%20and%20Artaxerxes%2C%20the%20kings%20of%20Persia.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_6_15%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20Temple%20was%20completed%20on%20March%26%23xA0%3B12%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E6%3A15%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Aramaic%20%3Cem%3Eon%20the%20third%20day%20of%20the%20month%20Adar%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20ancient%20Hebrew%20lunar%20calendar.%20A%20number%20of%20events%20in%20Ezra%20can%20be%20cross-checked%20with%20dates%20in%20surviving%20Persian%20records%20and%20related%20accurately%20to%20our%20modern%20calendar.%20This%20day%20was%20March%26%23xA0%3B12%2C%20515%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-sc%22%3Eb.c.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20during%20the%20sixth%20year%20of%20King%20Darius%26%23x2019%3Bs%20reign.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_6_16%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20Temple%20of%20God%20was%20then%20dedicated%20with%20great%20joy%20by%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%2C%20the%20priests%2C%20the%20Levites%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20people%20who%20had%20returned%20from%20exile.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_6_17%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EDuring%20the%20dedication%20ceremony%20for%20the%20Temple%20of%20God%2C%20100%26%23xA0%3Byoung%20bulls%2C%20200%26%23xA0%3Brams%2C%20and%20400%26%23xA0%3Bmale%20lambs%20were%20sacrificed.%20And%2012%26%23xA0%3Bmale%20goats%20were%20presented%20as%20a%20sin%20offering%20for%20the%20twelve%20tribes%20of%20Israel.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezra_6_18%22%20bk%3D%22ezra%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20priests%20and%20Levites%20were%20divided%20into%20their%20various%20divisions%20to%20serve%20at%20the%20Temple%20of%20God%20in%20Jerusalem%2C%20as%20prescribed%20in%20the%20Book%20of%20Moses.%3C%2Fverse_exp